<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <!-- Google fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rubik+Glitch&family=Russo+One&family=Saira+Stencil+One&family=Ubuntu+Condensed&family=Unica+One&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <!-- AOS  -->
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.2/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/user/viewPost.css" />

    <title>Notification</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="row bg bg-light p-3 rounded shadow-lg">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <a href="<%= post.banner %>" target="_blank">
            <img src="<%= post.banner %>" class="banner mt-3" alt="" />
          </a>
          <div class="detail-container">
            <span
              ><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-danger fs-1"></i><br />
              <span class="location"><%= post.state %></span></span
            >
            <span
              ><i
                class="bi bi-calendar-fill me-2 fs-1"
                style="color: rgb(210, 220, 220)"
              ></i
              ><br /><b class="date"> <%= post.date %></b></span
            >
            <span
              ><i class="bi bi-alarm-fill fs-1 me-2 text-secondary"></i><br /><b
                class="date"
              >
                <%= post.time %></b
              ></span
            >
            <span
              ><i class="bi bi-person-fill fs-1 me-2 text-secondary"></i
              ><br /><b class="date"> <%= post.guest %></b></span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content col-md-6 mt-3">
          <b class="title fs-1"><%= post.name %></b><br />
          <!-- <b class="description">Description: </b> -->
          <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Error
            dolores quas itaque sint perferendis quam reiciendis facilis,
            corrupti esse, ullam unde, cum delectus ea expedita cumque
            praesentium quae nisi at. Fuga odio facere sint fugit incidunt
            officiis, reiciendis, optio, labore eveniet quo quidem. Vitae ea
            voluptatum unde, odio, sapiente dolore praesentium quia corrupti
            nulla quis laudantium explicabo mollitia eum maxime! Quaerat tempora
            eum vel, fuga magnam, id consequuntur consectetur voluptatem unde
            aspernatur quasi accusantium obcaecati aliquam molestias quae a?
            Culpa corrupti magnam adipisci, ipsum vel asperiores esse autem
            omnis obcaecati! Nulla, tenetur. Quae nisi tempora dolorum cum
            reprehenderit mollitia fugiat, quo unde dolores enim ipsam nostrum
            suscipit in neque, vitae quibusdam consectetur explicabo ut animi
            odit! Aliquam esse quibusdam doloremque? Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet
            consectetur adipisicing elit. Modi excepturi magni temporibus
            facilis sunt laudantium itaque neque quis explicabo magnam, iure
            voluptas corporis porro. Repellendus voluptate voluptatem sapiente
            quibusdam quo. Consequuntur neque id perspiciatis, tempore repellat
            eaque nobis. Perspiciatis nostrum quod cumque, sint velit odit!
            Fugit eius error labore harum blanditiis pariatur expedita eaque
            eligendi maxime, vel sint voluptas ducimus. Expedita fugit mollitia
            deleniti omnis dolores eaque rerum nesciunt aperiam officia quaerat,
            illum nemo provident rem? Repudiandae voluptas sint cumque beatae
            itaque possimus fugiat eaque cum perspiciatis maxime! Laboriosam,
            eaque.
          </p>
          <div class="mb-3" style="display: flex; justify-content: flex-start">
            <% if (post.fee == 'Free') { %>
            <span class="me-2 badge bg text-light bg-success"
              ><%= post.fee%></span
            >
            <% }else{ %>
            <span class="me-2 badge bg text-light bg-danger"
              ><%= post.fee%></span
            >
            <% } %> <% if (post.mode == 'Online') { %>
            <span class="me-2 badge bg text-light bg-primary"
              ><%= post.mode%></span
            >
            <% }else{ %>
            <span class="me-2 badge bg text-light bg-secondary"
              ><%= post.mode%></span
            >
            <% } %> <% if (post.type == 'Hackathons') { %>
            <span
              class="me-2 badge bg text-light bg-info"
              style="background-color: bisque"
              ><%= post.type%></span
            >
            <% }else if(post.type == 'Conferences'){ %>
            <span class="me-2 badge bg text-light bg-warning"
              ><%= post.type%></span
            >
            <% }else if(post.type == 'Meetups'){ %>
            <span class="me-2 badge bg text-light bg-dark"
              ><%= post.type%></span
            >
            <% }else if(post.type == 'Webinars'){ %>
            <span class="me-2 badge" style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 247)"
              ><%= post.type%></span
            >
            <% }else{ %>
            <span
              class="me-2 badge text-light"
              style="background-color: rgb(255, 140, 0)"
              ><%= post.type%></span
            >
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="<%= post.link %>" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary"
          >Register Now</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
      AOS.init();
    </script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
